attributes.action: Urge the Israel Government to allow fuel, electricity and food into Gaza
attributes.additional_details: The people of Gaza are innocent and caught up in a war they did not choose to be collateral to.
attributes.background: The UK Government should urge the Israeli Government to stop the blockade of Food, Fuel and Electricity to the already impoverished city of Gaza
